{"tid":874223,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全連登最高質笑話 (唔笑即切柒)","createTime":"2018-10-24T04:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T08:39:56.000Z","uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e4a37201e17b804af1b53332009b983aa91ec4","tid":874223,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"首先，要跟住做d 步驟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺右手邊度噤個 lockscreen 制<br />\n等十秒先入返黎呢個post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n準備好？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOK, 歡迎返黎 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱先見唔見到...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你自己個樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果見到你自己咁大個笑話都唔笑就去切柒吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0622a837582ba8726a1ed26339fd244c3a929fa4","tid":874223,"uid":57895,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"切柒未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"